   "author_association" : "MEMBER",
   "body" : "The wallet does not mark the replaced tx as out-of-mempool. This causes failures in user scripts, because later RPCs may depend on this state change from `bumpfee`.\r\n\r\n\r\nFor example, the following might fail on current master:\r\n\r\n```\r\ntxid = sendtoaddress(...)\r\nbumpfee(txid)\r\nabandontransaction(txid)  # fails because txid is still marked as \"in mempool\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nFixes #18831",
